\cf2 Skip to 2 minutes and 36 seconds\
}}\pard\pardeftab720\sl260\sa326\partightenfactor0
\cf3 We're going to randomly select people, one at a time, until we get 25 of them. When a person get selected their dot turns black. Here they are being selected now.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl260\sa326\partightenfactor0
{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/data-to-insight/8/steps/508378#"}}{\fldrslt 
