\pard\pardeftab720\sl260\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Skip to 2 minutes and 51 seconds\
}}\pard\pardeftab720\sl260\sa326\partightenfactor0
\cf3 Now we're going to make a plot using just those people selected and mark the position of their mean. Well, we got that wrong. The real mean is 118.1, but our sample gave about 121. We'll try again and see if we can do better.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl260\sa326\partightenfactor0
