\cf3 Just as bad as last time, but on the other side. Every time we do this we're going to leave a blue mark at the position of the new sample mean. This will build up a history of all the sample means we've seen. Let's do it a third time.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl260\sa326\partightenfactor0
