\cf2 Skip to 3 minutes and 36 seconds\
}}\pard\pardeftab720\sl260\sa326\partightenfactor0
\cf3 Even worse. Of course, in the real world, we sample when we can't see our population and don't know the real answer. So we'll put a veil over the population to make it a little more realistic and do it five more times.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl260\sa326\partightenfactor0
