\cf2 Skip to 6 minutes and 9 seconds\
}}\pard\pardeftab720\sl260\sa326\partightenfactor0
\cf3 The good news is that the set of answers we've got with the bigger samples are generally much closer to the truth. We're making small errors.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl260\sa326\partightenfactor0
{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/data-to-insight/8/steps/508378#"}}{\fldrslt 
